attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Absolutely charming single family townhouse located just off of newly renovated Thomas Park in South Boston. This 3+ / 4 bedroom home offers residents a convenient floor plan with a parlor-level kitchen and entertaining floor. The high ceilings and crown moldings give this space charm and character and the West - facing windows let natural light pour in. The kitchen is complete with classic shaker cabinets, a center island with storage, mosaic marble floors and windows looking over the private patio below. Host family and friends effortlessly across four levels of living and two amazing, private outdoor spaces. The roof deck is stunning and is accessed by a head house for convenience and ease. Views of the city stretch out in 360 degrees from this commanding deck.  There is a full basement for a work bench, Thule racks, bikes, skis and building utilities. Walk to the best of South Boston in this central location but enjoy it all from a quiet side street.
